{"tid":1288273,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要求釋放梁天琦！！！！","createTime":"2019-07-05T14:25:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T03:55:39.000Z","uid":54163,"like":345,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"c999d2d2407f6b9ef13e8a98e054fa7cc15d2951","tid":1288273,"uid":54163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:25:52.000Z","msg":"睇番天琦以前既訪問 佢真係行得太前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就係知道港共政府唔可信 所以先不惜一切奮身一搏<br />\n港大哲學系出身 唔敢話佢本身前途無可限量<br />\n但就係因為犯左所謂暴動 要囚6年<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">預計2022年1月19日出獄</span></span><br />\n佢究竟做錯咩？我相信佢絕對係諗過度過先願意留守係香港承擔後果 佢大可以跟埋黃台仰去德國政治庇護 但佢冇咁樣做到 佢依然堅信香港人總有一日會覺醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我知佢係獄中都會睇到新聞 知道612有成200萬人上街抗爭一定好感動 <br />\n但係 我真係好怕佢係獄中捱唔住 仲有3年時間<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">梁天琦，係香港人對你唔住</span></span><br />\n多謝你<br />\n救得一個得一個"},{"pid":"17372e56741d8ff6b248b0662ba6802910756e34","tid":1288273,"uid":268410,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:26:50.000Z","msg":"而家睇返佢講既野 <br />\n真係每一句都好岩 經過6月感受好深"},{"pid":"9359a4ee713efc53f97b99152590bc97eed4714a","tid":1288273,"uid":268410,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:27:15.000Z","msg":"真係走得太前"},{"pid":"ba2c7a4623b90190f5695563373fb373148c59ad","tid":1288273,"uid":74711,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:28:03.000Z","msg":"釋放梁天琦！"},{"pid":"8d0799cc8018fd73f8e1923bd6621d8af40fa97b","tid":1288273,"uid":9813,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:28:13.000Z","msg":"天琦講嘅嘢應驗晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a7f8489f9cdc4de847b62f7df8f09b724a20bc","tid":1288273,"uid":54163,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T14:28:57.000Z","msg":"好想可